{"tid":2173750,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【檢測大龍鳳】百佳Aeon員工投訴「被自願」檢測憂失私隱 「唔想為政府湊數」","createTime":"2020-08-25T12:09:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T16:48:43.000Z","uid":58335,"like":34,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"876202f6cda674654850807fc474da9b57633ab8","tid":2173750,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:09:20.000Z","msg":"陸續有企業呼籲員工參與政府的較高風險群組自願檢測計劃，其中百佳超巿及Aeon均有員工踢爆計劃並非自願性質，Aeon部門主管甚至威脅，「唔做檢測就等同唔再報更」，令前線人心惶惶。有員工表明擔心個人資料、DNA資料等會被港府掌握，同時不希望為政府計劃「湊數」，「好似好多人支持去驗咁」。<br />\n<br />\n網上近日流傳一份由超級市場百佳發出的通告，指公司將會參與食環署提供的「2019冠狀病毒病檢測服務」，署方會委託Prenetics Limited為員工提供免費檢測；通告雖指檢測屬「自願性質」，「衷心呼籲各同事積極參與」，惟有員工向《蘋果》反映，指分店經理要求。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200825/NFJFBKWBIVDWLLMOSXEN4NQGIE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200825%2FNFJFBKWBIVDWLLMOSXEN4NQGIE%2F&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXZ1QB7Ma9ovE6nvZW%2BRTqP4%3D&h=c7dbb21d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200825%2FNFJFBKWBIVDWLLMOSXEN4NQGIE%2F&h=4f0cf2b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200825/NFJFBKWBIVDWLLMOSXEN4NQGIE/</a>"},{"pid":"2405a04fb4327d779f98a37269d49fc45e10209f","tid":2173750,"uid":231583,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:11:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b669f49784b9734f2ba2498a0498f9b948f8d1ac","tid":2173750,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:11:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f66632aa29550c870a6baa0e37bac116696b52e4","tid":2173750,"uid":254450,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12